Meet Wache Gordon aka Wache G.

A Gospel Artist, Singer, Songwriter, Instrumentalist and Music minister.

Born as the third child of 6 to Rev & Past Mrs Wache Emmanuel on the 28th Of March 1996 in Nkambe. He hails from Fonfuka(Bum) in the North West Region of Cameroon.

As a teenager, Gordon became born again and was baptized on the 4th of April 2010.

He has served instrumentalist from a tender age at Berean Baptist church Kumba Cameroon where he equally honed his singing gifts.

Wache G Discovered His singing Potential in 2017 When he served as a music Tutor and teacher at Covenant Baptist Church.

Wache Gordon Obtained his Ordinary and advance level certificate at B.H.S NDOP and later Proceeded to the university in 2015 Were he studied Software Engineering at Landmark university College.

And later moved to the university of Buea Where he obtained a Degree. Gordon holds a Bsc in Software Engineering from the University of Buea.

Wache G presently fellowships at Christland Ministries Buea were he serves as a Church administrator.

He was recently Signed to Rochie Osvalin's Worship Nation

Check him out on his pages : Wache G

<!--EndFragment-->
